{"tid":308751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（投錯胎）支那母抱兒拍洪水誤鬆手 一歲兒摔進急流被沖走","createTime":"2017-07-04T12:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T12:37:27.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b340db39839dfdc0a496e5fe779216412e21577","tid":308751,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:31:54.000Z","msg":"糊塗母抱兒拍洪水誤鬆手 一歲兒摔進急流被沖走<br />\n湖南各地近日因為水流暴漲，各地都有洪水災情傳出。一名抱著一歲兒的糊塗媽媽，為了拿手機拍洪水，卻一個不小心將小孩從懷裡掉入洪水中被沖走，家屬當場崩潰痛哭。雖然事後警方趕到現場，但小孩已被洪水沖到不見蹤影。據傳此事是發生在湖南安江，不過當地警方隨即發出聲明表示，此事並非發生在湖南安江，影片中出現的警察也不是他們。<br />\n從民眾側拍的影片中可見，畫面中的女子蹲在地上痛哭失聲，旁邊則有不少民眾圍著她安撫，也有其他家屬及民眾情緒激動的向警方要求救人，但由於洪水實在太湍急，警方也無能為力，孩子恐怕是凶多吉少。<br />\n<br />\n影片在網路上曝光後，不少網友紛紛無奈留言「洪水有什麼好拍的，孩子真無辜」、「這種媽媽&hellip;就算這次沒事也會有下次」、「媽媽有毛病？洪水有什麼好拍」、「遇上這樣的媽，只能說小孩真可憐」、「完全沒有危機意識」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/203035_31e26706af42edbd99ccd0d23796851d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F203035_31e26706af42edbd99ccd0d23796851d.jpg&h=ee68a654&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/203036_bbde8ea6ad0cc86082e5f789ebd8a629.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F203036_bbde8ea6ad0cc86082e5f789ebd8a629.jpg&h=f75f5396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20170704003220-260803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhottopic.chinatimes.com%2F20170704003220-260803&d=lDLTLuHKMyJrukGQGB7UI%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=39552005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20170704003220-260803</a><br />\n個仔好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ad6034f20b99182a26495348b46a0f1360f013","tid":308751,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"支那社會風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}